                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Mobile</placeName>\n                <date>April 7 1851</date>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Respected Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Enclosed please<lb/> find $20.00 it being nine Dollars\n                subscription<lb/> of <persName>Israel H Jones</persName> &amp;c met. 4.00\n                    <sic>arrearrs</sic> &amp; the subscription<lb/> for the ensuing year. Please\n                take notice of the same<lb/> in the Occident. the Balance of 11.00 you will please\n                give<lb/> me credit for the Thalith. Other <add>?</add> I have not yet<lb/> made.\n                    <persName>Myer</persName> of <placeName>Montgomery</placeName> promises to send\n                me 6.00 which<lb/> is all he owes bal. <persName>Philip</persName> is at present\n                absent. You will do<lb/> me a favour by sending me a list of all your\n                subscribers<lb/> &amp; their <sic>indebtness</sic>; I have written to <persName>Mr.\n                    I Hart</persName>\n                <placeName>N. O.</placeName><lb/> for a statement of Books I recvd<add>?</add> from\n                him; &amp; if you will<lb/> let me know the amt you <add>?</add> from me for\n                Books<lb/> I shall forthwith send you the Blln if there is any<lb/> I have been so\n                careless that I have not taken any notice<lb/> of the money I sent you. The\n                    <add>חדושים</add> I have not yet<lb/> disposed of, but <persName>Mr\n                    Cohen</persName> told me last night that<lb/> he probably may take a\n                    <sic>sett</sic>. You will send a copie<add>?</add><lb/> of the Occident to J.\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\"><persName>Loewenstein</persName>\n                    <placeName>Marion Miss</placeName></hi>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3902024c/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
