                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>effect much good &amp; I am sure they all would hail<lb/> such an event with the\n                utmost delight &amp; pleasure I<lb/> rem more than your humble servant.—</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am my dear sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Yours very truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">B H Emanuel</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <add>חזן שוחט מלמד שו\"ש לק\"ק ש\"ש</add>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
